text:
🌳🪑Sungei Serangoon Park is a narrow green belt that lies between Sungei Serangoon Park Connector and Sengkang East Drive road.
🚶🧗A serene green lung for joggers and brisk walkers.
🏋️🚻A Fitness Corner and a clean functioning Toilet completes the small Park.
Fresh air and links to park connector linking you to north eastern parks. Great for running!
A park facilitating exercising access, greenery and for relaxing.
Scenic place for a walk or run
